---
import HTML from "../../layouts/HTML/HTML.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import VideoProduction from "../../assets/MediaTraningBanner.jpeg";
import MediaTraning from "../../assets/MediaTraning.jpg";
import BackGroundImage from "@components/BackGroundImage.astro";
import CrisisCommunications from "../../assets/CrisisCommunications1.jpg";
import Industry from "../../assets/Industry.jpg";
import MultiMedia from "../../assets/Multi-Media.jpg";
---

<Fragment>
  <HTML>
    <BackGroundImage imageSource={VideoProduction} text=" STRATEGIC CONSULTING" />

    <section class="container mx-auto lg:pt-24 sm:py-0">
      <div
        class=" flex md:flex-col-reverse lg:px-[200px] sm:flex-col-reverse sm:items-center lg:justify-between"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:text-2xl lg:max-w-[100%] md:max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[100%] lg:text-left md:text-center sm:text-left py-20 space-y-5"
        >
          <p class=" lg:text-center sm:text-left">
            Having covered politics, criminal justice, and business for decades,
            the team at <span class="font-[Poppins] font-bold">
              Media Advisory Experts</span
            > can offer C-suite executives, leaders in law enforcement, and
            local to multi - national corporations strategic consulting, crisis
            communications, news industry insight, public relations, and media
            coaching services to prepare them for an always - on media ecosystem
            that demands lightning, accurate respon se and accountability —
            while also ensuring their vital context breaks through the noise and
            is heard by their target audience
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container mx-auto lg:py-10 sm:py-10 sm:space-y-5">
      <h2
        class="lg:text-3xl md:text-3xl sm:text-2xl sm:pt-10 md:pt-0 font-semibold font-[Poppins] text-center lg:py-20"
      >
        EARNED MEDIA
      </h2>
      <div
        class=" lg:flex lg:px-[100px] lg:items-center lg:flex-row-reverse md:block sm:block lg:justify-between sm:space-y-10"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:text-2xl lg:max-w-[40%] md:max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[100%] lg:text-left md:text-center sm:text-left space-y-5"
        >
          <p>
            Our team has experience generating earned media coverage, both for
            an individual and for business. While some other firms believe
            blasting a news release to a hundred media outlets will do the
            trick, we know that isn’t an effective ROI. Instead, we’ve:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc">
            <li>
              De signed a database of media contacts to ensure the right target
              audience hears your message
            </li>
            <li>
              Built an agility to respond to a 24/7 digital media environment
            </li>
            <li>Developed tools to ensure media placement</li>
            <li>
              Created a process to streamline your message so it doesn’t get
              lost
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-[40rem]">
          <Image src={MediaTraning} alt="image" class="rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="container mx-auto lg:py-10 sm:py-10">
      <h2
        class="lg:text-3xl md:text-3xl sm:text-2xl sm:pt-10 md:pt-0 font-semibold font-[Poppins] text-center lg:py-20"
      >
        CRISIS COMMUNICATIONS
      </h2>
      <div
        class="lg:px-[100px] lg:flex lg:items-center md:block sm:block lg:justify-between"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:text-2xl lg:max-w-[40%] md:max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[100%] lg:text-left md:text-center sm:text-left space-y-5"
        >
          <p>
            Using o ur decades of media experience, vast network of contacts,
            and innovative methods, <span class="font-[Poppins] font-bold">
              Media Advisory Experts</span
            > can help prepare today’s leaders for tomorrow’s media storm — or
            respond in an instant when it lands at your doorstep. Sometimes,
            despite your best efforts, you can’t head off adverse publicity. But
            often, clients can get in front of the headline, crafting a message
            that limits reputational damage and busines s impact. The key is
            speed. Don’t wait to prepare your business or brand ; contact us
            today
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-[40rem]">
          <Image src={CrisisCommunications} alt="image" class="rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="lg:py-10 container mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="lg:text-3xl md:text-3xl sm:text-2xl sm:pt-10 md:pt-0 font-semibold font-[Poppins] text-center lg:py-20"
      >
        NEWS INDUSTRY INSIGHT
      </h2>
      <div
        class=" lg:px-[100px] lg:flex lg:items-center lg:flex-row-reverse md:block sm:block lg:justify-between"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:text-2xl lg:max-w-[40%] md:max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[100%] lg:text-left md:text-center sm:text-left space-y-5"
        >
          <p>
            With new digital media brands created all the time and legacy
            properties reinventing themselves or fading , <span
              class="font-[Poppins] font-bold"
            >
              Media Advisory Experts
            </span>can provide key context into the current media landscape –
            and insight what it will look like in the quarters ahead. With
            information and knowledge comes an ability to adapt, to mold your
            message for maximum effect and impact. Use our knowledge of the news
            industry to position your brand for success.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-[40rem]">
          <Image src={Industry} alt="image" class="rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="lg:pt-10 lg:pb-20 container mx-auto">
      <h2
        class="lg:text-3xl md:text-3xl sm:text-2xl sm:pt-10 md:pt-0 font-semibold font-[Poppins] text-center lg:py-20"
      >
        MULTI-MEDIA
      </h2>
      <div
        class=" lg:px-[100px] lg:flex lg:items-center md:block sm:block lg:justify-between"
      >
        <div
          class="lg:text-2xl lg:max-w-[40%] md:max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-[100%] lg:text-left md:text-center sm:text-left space-y-5"
        >
          <p>
            The experts at <span class="font-[Poppins] font-bold">
              Media Advisory Experts
            </span> can advise you on a multi-media strategy to generate broad
            exposure for your message, brand, or crisis response. With
            innovative techniques and a shrewd understanding of the evolving
            digital media landscape, our team can expertly position you for
            success across platforms, no matter where your audience consumes
            their media.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:max-w-[40rem]">
          <Image src={MultiMedia} alt="image" class="rounded-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mx-auto lg:pt-20 lg:px-[100px]">
        <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">
          Contact us today: <br />
          <span class="lg:text-2xl sm:text-sm font-[Poppins] text-blue"
            ><a href="mailto:contact@mediaadvisoryexperts.com"
              >contact@mediaadvisoryexperts.com</a
            >
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </HTML>
</Fragment>
